CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 19, 1956, pg. B13 reads: "Masters Of Ceremonies - The Rev. Leroy Patrick and Mrs. Ethel Ramos Harris took charge of the pageant and introduced the debutantes."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of LeRoy Patrick and Ethel Ramos Harris walking through interior with audience of people on right, for Alpha Kapp Alpha's Fifth Debutante Cotillion, Syria Mosque
